- Conv Block 1 : 64 filters
- Conv Block 2 : 128 filters
- Conv Block 3 : 256 filters

### Performance

- Validation Accuracy : 84.7%
- Classes :
    - Stress
    - Non Stress

### Quantization Variants

- FP32
- FP16
- QINT8
- FLOAT8 (Simulated)
- FLOAT4 (Simulated)
- QINT4 (Simulated)

### Deployment

- FP16 → GPU Realtime
- QINT8 → CPU Lightweight
""")